{MEM-180, CHECK, MEM_EYE} - HA (Headache): Diffuse+variable = Rx/anxiety/tension/migraine. Sev+sudden+1-side = HZO/sinusitis/ON/AACG/aneurysm/GCA. AM up/PM down+nausea = SOL/IIH/ICP.
